  "text": "For construction of new constructs 1 and 2, the plasmids were re-arranged such pGAL1 and T CYC1 were deleted, and bacterial parts were left out upon digestion prior to yeast transformation. Nat ORF sub-regions were amplified using PCR. NatMX cassette, KanMX cassette from pYM13 plasmid [CITATION_1] , or LEU2 cassette from YIplac128 plasmid were used for selection in yeast transformation.",
